Diva Festive 3/4 Sleeve Printed Women's Kurti Price: Rs.399

Sometimes simple is all you want! This kurta is one such garment with an all over print in a contrasting colour and shadow stripes. Sequins embellish the neckline to add a hint of glamour! Wear this with metallic leggings and mojaris!
